Token generated & stored
      ↓
Email service called
      ↓
SMTP/API request made
      ↓
Email provider receives
      ↓
Email delivered to inbox
      ↓
User clicks link
      ↓
Token validated
```

---

## Breakpoint Analysis

### 1. Token Generation & Storage Layer

```javascript
// BREAK POINT: Token never persisted before email sends
